parameters:
It seems that the water flow is connected to the outside.... Will
you jump in?

I said there was nothing here, and yet you still came...? You're
quite curious, aren't you...

Too bad! There's nothing here, you know... But it's kind of
pitiful, so I'll give you my treasure as a present.
We must treat customers like you with care...
なにかしらのアイテムゲット

No, there's nothing more here! Just go back to that sparkling
place...!
